txt.en: 'Everyone must pay tribute to me as I lead them to riches and power. Collect tribute from those who have not paid up!'
'Of course they have paid. They all seek to follow me down this path of greatness!'
Collect tribute from those in Fushaum Bal North ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
You should collect tribute from those in Fushaum Bal North.
The Khundolar Commander can be found at Fushaum Bal North.\n\nYou should talk to the Khundolar Commander.
The encampment of Fushaum Bal is a lawless home to evil men once under the command of Sauron.
